{{Infobox journal | title = International Journal of Science and Mathematics Education | cover = Cover - issue 7(2) - IntJSciMathEduc.jpg | editor = Huann-shyang Lin | discipline = [[Science education]], [[mathematics education]] | formernames = | abbreviation = Int. J. Sci. Math. Educ. | publisher = [[Springer Science+Business Media]] on behalf of the [[National Science Council|National Science Council of Taiwan]] | country = | frequency = Bimonthly | history = 2004–present | openaccess = | license = | impact = 0.460 | impact-year = 2012 | website = https://www.springer.com/education+%26+language/mathematics+education/journal/10763 | link1 = https://link.springer.com/journal/10763 | link1-name = Online access | link2 = https://link.springer.com/journal/volumesAndIssues/10763 | link2-name = Online archive | JSTOR = | OCLC = 474774121 | LCCN = | CODEN = | ISSN = 1571-0068 | eISSN = 1573-1774 }} The '''''International Journal of Science and Mathematics Education''''' is a bimonthly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] published by [[Springer Science+Business Media]] on behalf of the [[National Science Council|National Science Council of Taiwan]]. It covers [[science education|science]] and [[mathematics education]] topics and research methods, particularly ones with cross-curricular dimensions or which explore the area from different cultural perspectives.<ref name = aims>{{cite web |url=https://www.springer.com/education+%26+language/mathematics+education/journal/10763?detailsPage=aboutThis |title=About this journal |accessdate = July 19, 2013 |work=International Journal of Science and Mathematics Education |publisher = [[Springer Science+Business Media]]}}</ref> The journal was established in 2004 with Fou-Lai Lin ([[National Taiwan Normal University]]) as [[editor-in-chief]]; {{As of|2013|7|lc=yes}} the position is held by Huann-shyang Lin ([[National Sun Yat-sen University]]).
