{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}

'''''Pioneers of Science''''' ({{lang-tr|Bilimin öncüleri}}) ({{ISBN|9786055888039}}) is a book by [[Cemal Yıldırım]] which has run to 22 editions.<ref>{{cite news |title=Prof. Yıldırım hayatını kaybetti |url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/Guncel/HaberDetay.aspx?aType=HaberDetay&Kategori=guncel&KategoriID=24&ArticleID=1074701&Date=24.03.2009&b=Prof.%20Yildirim%20hayatini%20kaybetti |work=[[Milliyet]] |date=24 March 2009 |accessdate=15 February 2010 }}</ref> The book explains the scientific method with anecdotes from significant figures in scientific history such as [[Albert Einstein]], [[Niels Bohr]] and [[Marie Curie]].

